snippet.title: Arkanoid ZX Spectrum
snippet.description: Great conversion of the most famous of the breakout clones......and I really thought I suck so badly at these type of games, turns out I was bluffing all along......well okay it's still not brilliant but it exceeded my expectations anyway.
